            "title": "Variation of dipteran ectoparasites (Streblidae) on Anoura geoffroyi Gray, 1838 (Phyllostomidae) in two caves in southeastern Brazil",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Aline",
                    "lastName": "Da Silva Reis"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Robson",
                    "lastName": "De Almeida Zampaulo"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
